    "summary": "I am a native english-speaking language specialist from South Africa, now living in The Netherlands. My 17 years of work experience includes professional journalism, public relations and corporate communications in a variety of industries. I specialise in telling stories and helping my clients to find the right words to communicate their message. \n\nMy core strength as a language professional is versatility. I enjoy the precision required to write about business, finance and science. I can also comfortably spend hours improving the clarity of documents, proposals and articles. However, I also enjoy travel writing or features of high-profile individuals which allows more creative flair. \n\nWriting Expertise: Business, financial services, consumer finance, insurance, agriculture, environment, science & technology, agriculture, corporate social investment, marketing, brand communication, travel & lifestyle, social media, blogging, creative writing. \n\nLanguage Services: Copy editing, proofreading, copywriting, web writing, distilling technical information into plain english, ghost writing, SEO copywriting, translation. \n\nPlease visit my website, www.wordguru.nl, to see my portfolio, who I have worked for and what I can do.\nI also have my own travel and lifestyle blog. Please take a look. www.wheresthat.nl\n\n",
